# Frontend — Vue {{VUE_VERSION}} / {{FRAMEWORK}}

## COMPONENT RULES
- DO: Composition API with `<script setup>` — NEVER Options API for new components
- DO: Single-file components (`.vue`) — template → script → style order
- DO: Place components in `{{COMPONENTS_DIR}}/` — PascalCase filenames
- DO NOT: Use `any` type — define explicit prop types with `defineProps<{...}>()`

## ROUTING ({{ROUTING_PATTERN}})
- Routes live in `{{ROUTES_DIR}}/`
- {{ROUTING_NOTE}}
<!-- ROUTING_NOTE example for Nuxt: "File-based routing; use definePageMeta() for route metadata" -->

## COMPOSABLES
- Place in `{{COMPOSABLES_DIR}}/` — prefix with `use` (e.g. `useAuth`, `useCart`)
- NEVER duplicate logic available as a composable — search `{{COMPOSABLES_DIR}}/` first

## STYLING ({{STYLING_SYSTEM}})
- DO: {{STYLING_RULE}}
<!-- STYLING_RULE example: "Scoped styles in <style scoped> using Tailwind utilities" -->
- Shared styles live in `{{STYLES_DIR}}/`

## STATE MANAGEMENT ({{STATE_LIBRARY}})
- Store files in `{{STORES_DIR}}/`
- {{STATE_PATTERN}}
<!-- STATE_PATTERN example for Pinia: "Use defineStore with setup syntax; prefer composables over stores for component-local state" -->

